username: user name should not contain whitespaces
password: Min. 8 characters, should include 1 letter and 1 number
orgunit: Use Org Unit ID to avoid errors
phone_number: The phone number as a string (in single or double quote). It has to start with the country code like +1 for US
editable_org_unit_types: Use comma separated Org Unit Type IDs to avoid errors: 1, 2
